### Dark Mode (Dashboard only)

Dark mode is toggled via the Tailwind `dark:` variant:
- Backgrounds: `dark:bg-gray-900`, `dark:bg-gray-950`
- Text: `dark:text-gray-100`, `dark:text-white`
- Borders: `dark:border-white/10`
- Hover: `dark:hover:bg-white/10`
- Shadows: `dark:shadow-none`

