## Spacing & Layout Constants

- **Standard padding scale:** `px-3` (12), `px-3.5` (14), `px-4` (16), `px-6` (24)
- **Standard gap scale:** `gap-2` (8), `gap-3` (12), `gap-4` (16), `gap-6` (24), `gap-9` (36)
- **Button height:** `h-11` (44px)
- **Responsive padding pattern:** `px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-6`
- **Content max-width (forms):** `max-w-[640px]`

---

## Border Radius Scale

| Size | Class | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| 6px | `rounded-md` | Inputs, small buttons, nav items |
| 8px | `rounded-lg` | Cards, dropdowns |
| 12px | `rounded-xl` | Form cards, containers |
| 16px | `rounded-2xl` | Hero cards, modals, signature canvas |
| Full | `rounded-full` | Avatars, icon buttons, pill badges |
| Pill | `rounded-[512px]` | Status badges |

