## Shadow Scale

| Name | Class | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| XS | `shadow-xs` | Buttons, cards, sticky headers |
| Ring | `ring-1 ring-gray-200` | Subtle outline borders |
| Elevated | `shadow-[-3px_20px_25px_-5px_rgba(0,0,0,0.10),0_10px_10px_-5px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)]` | Feature/payment cards |

---

## Transitions & Animation

- **Standard transition:** `transition-colors` or `transition-all`
- **Fast (hover):** `duration-200`
- **Normal (UI state):** `duration-300 ease-out`
- **Slow (expand/collapse):** `duration-400 ease-in-out`
- **Modal enter:** `data-enter:duration-300 data-enter:ease-out`
- **Modal leave:** `data-leave:duration-200 data-leave:ease-in`
- **Modal closed state:** `data-closed:translate-y-4 data-closed:opacity-0`
- **Sidebar expand:** `max-h-0 opacity-0 pointer-events-none` → expanded with `transition-all duration-400 ease-in-out`

---

## Z-Index Strategy

| Layer | Value | Element |
|---|---|---|
| Sticky header | `z-40` | Top nav bar |
| Sidebar toggle | `z-[70]` | Collapse/expand button |
| Mobile sidebar | `z-[70]` | Off-canvas drawer |
| Modal backdrop | Default stacking | Dialog element |

