# ONBOARDING STYLE

> Screens: Welcome, Confirm Identity, Confirm Business Details, Review Documents, Signature, Payment
> Location: `src/pages/onboarding/`

## Layout

- **Container:** `h-screen` or `min-h-screen`, flex row
- **Two-column split:**
  - Left sidebar: `w-[325px] shrink-0` (fixed, does not scroll)
  - Right content: `flex-1 flex flex-col min-h-0 overflow-y-auto`
- **Outer background:** `bg-gray-200`
- **Inner content area:** White card, `max-w-[640px]` centered

## Onboarding Sidebar (Left Column)

- **Background:** `bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1E326F] to-[#090C38]`
- **Padding:** `p-[56px]`
- **Gap between items:** `gap-[35px]`
- **Text color:** `text-white`
- **Logo:** Top area with SMART Hub branding and yellow gradient accent

### Stepper Navigation

- **Completed step:** White checkmark SVG inside a circle, clickable
- **Current step:** Ring indicator — `ring-white/20` outer, `ring-white` inner dot, `aria-current="step"`
- **Upcoming step:** Small dot `size-2 rounded-full`, muted `text-white/30`, hover brightens to `text-white`
- **Connecting lines:** Implied by vertical gap and step ordering
- **Transitions:** Smooth color transitions on hover

## Welcome Screen (Hero)

- **Hero card:** `bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1E326F] to-[#090C38] rounded-2xl p-10 relative overflow-hidden`
- **Decorative circles:** Three concentric circles positioned absolutely with `bg-[rgba(47,104,237,0.10)]`, sizes descending (1235px → 783px → 331px), offset to top-right with negative positioning
- **Greeting:** `text-2xl font-bold text-white` title, `text-white/60 text-lg` subtitle
- **Notification card:** `bg-white/15 ring-[8px] ring-white/5 rounded-[10px] p-4 text-white/80 text-sm`
- **Footer:** Transcard branding with `text-[#0089CF]`, legal links in muted text

## Form Screens (Identity / Business Details)

- **Form card:** `rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6`
- **Field spacing:** `space-y-4` between fields
- **Field groups:** Label → `mt-2` → Input
- **Two-column fields:** `grid grid-cols-2 gap-4` where appropriate
- **Action bar:** `flex items-center gap-6` with Back (secondary, `flex-1`) and Next (primary, `flex-1 h-11`)

## Document Review Screen

- **Document list container:** `divide-y divide-gray-100 rounded-md border border-gray-200`
- **Document row:** `py-4 pr-5 pl-4`, flex layout, file icon `size-5 text-gray-400`, filename `truncate font-medium text-gray-900`, size `text-xs text-gray-400`
- **Review link:** `text-blue-600` inline action
- **PDF modal:** `sm:max-w-4xl rounded-2xl bg-white`, iframe `h-[60vh] rounded-md border border-gray-200`

## Signature Screen

- **Tab bar:** `space-x-4`, active `bg-gray-100 text-gray-900`, inactive `text-gray-500`
- **Canvas area:** `h-[296px] w-full rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4 relative`
- **Clear button:** `absolute top-4 right-4`, secondary button style

## Payment Screen

- **Amount card:** `bg-[linear-gradient(108deg,#3773FF_3.3%,#2254CA_99.23%)] rounded-2xl px-8 py-10 text-white relative overflow-hidden`
- **Decorative circles:** 3 absolute-positioned circles with `bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(2,28,73,0.13)_0%,rgba(2,28,73,0)_100%)]`, rotated `rotate-[-105deg]`
- **Action pills:** 3-column `rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-3 py-2 hover:bg-gray-200`, icon `text-blue-600`
- **Payment method rows:** `rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-3 hover:bg-gray-50`, left icon in `w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-gray-50`, right chevron with hover translate

