# DASHBOARD STYLE

> Screens: SMART Exchange Dashboard (and future dashboard pages)
> Location: `src/pages/dashboard/`

## Layout

- **Fixed sidebar + offset content:**
  - Sidebar: `w-[360px]` fixed to left, full height, visible at `lg:` breakpoint
  - Content: `lg:pl-[360px]` to offset for sidebar
- **Mobile sidebar:** Off-canvas dialog, slides in from left with `data-closed:-translate-x-full`, backdrop `bg-gray-900/80`
- **Sticky header:** `sticky top-0 z-40 border-b border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-xs`

## Dashboard Sidebar

- **Background:** `bg-white dark:bg-gray-900`
- **Scrollable:** `overflow-y-auto`
- **Section dividers:** `h-px bg-gray-200 dark:bg-white/10`
- **Sidebar toggle button:** `fixed top-[30px] left-[344px] z-[70] rounded-sm bg-white px-1 py-1 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/10`

### Navigation Items

```
h-10 rounded-md px-2 text-base font-medium flex items-center gap-3
text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-100 hover:text-gray-900
transition-colors cursor-pointer
dark:text-gray-300 dark:hover:bg-white/10 dark:hover:text-white
```

- **Nav icon:** `size-6 shrink-0 text-gray-500 group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:text-gray-400 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400`
- **Active state:** `bg-gray-100 text-gray-900 dark:bg-white/10 dark:text-white`
- **Expandable submenu:** Chevron rotates, children at `ml-9`, expand via `max-h-0 opacity-0` → full height with `transition-all duration-400 ease-in-out`

## Header Bar

- **Layout:** `sticky top-0 z-40 px-4 pt-4 pb-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-6 lg:pt-6`
- **Background:** `bg-white border-b border-gray-200 shadow-xs dark:bg-gray-900 dark:shadow-none dark:border-white/10`
- **Hamburger (mobile):** `lg:hidden` with `size-6 text-gray-700`
- **Greeting:** `text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white`
- **Business selector:** `hidden sm:flex`, pill-style with chevron
- **Notification bell:** `size-6` icon button with hover effects
- **Profile avatar:** Circular `size-8 rounded-full`, dropdown on click

## Dashboard Content Area

- **Responsive padding:** `px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-6`
- **Card grid:** Standard card component with `rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-white/10`
- **Tables/lists:** `divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-white/10`

